reviewText:
Release date is 2016 probably on video-of ANY type. Actual year it was made must have been 1995.
Right from the get go, the narrator's way of talking, I knew this video was old!
It's a nice, slow paced video if you want to know some past history and the land. It's in-depth enough but as the review said, outdated. I just can't figure out what year it's made though. No cell phones, the clothes, etc..
No year in credits either....I looked hard! And this bugs me.
